oai_dc:dc.dc:title: anti-2,19-diethoxycarbonyl-2,19-diformyl-amino[3.2.3.2]paracyclophane
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: DAMODHARAN, L
IBRAHIM, BS
PATTABHI, V
HALDER, S
KOTHA, S
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: The title compound, C42H46N2O6, crystallizes with half a molecule in the asymmetric unit, the molecule being centrosymmetric. The ethyl ester and N-formyl side chains attached to the C-alpha atom of the molecule adopt a trans and cis configuration, respectively. The crystal structure is stabilized by C-H...O, N-H...O and C-H...pi interactions and herring-bone-type packing is observed.
